Date:   Wed Mar 23 17:44:16 2011 +0100

    zmq_device removed
    
    Devices are basically applications on top of 0MQ stack. They
    should reside in separate libraties.
    
    Signed-off-by: Martin Sustrik <sustrik@250bpm.com>

